WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 34=

01:49.690 --> 01:50.530
Zhao.

01:51.020 --> 01:51.860
Zhao?

01:58.050 --> 01:59.410
You've slept for days.

02:00.130 --> 02:01.380
If I hadn't come,

02:03.260 --> 02:04.290
you would be dead.

02:14.410 --> 02:15.980
That man in black is strong.

02:17.220 --> 02:18.500
How did you escape?

02:19.410 --> 02:20.410
I have my ways.

02:22.980 --> 02:23.820
Here.

02:24.290 --> 02:25.130
Take medicine.

02:44.010 --> 02:45.220
Smiley.

02:45.820 --> 02:46.730
Not as good as yours.

02:47.610 --> 02:48.660
Just make do.

03:02.170 --> 03:03.010
Zhao,

03:05.780 --> 03:07.940
the man in black

03:09.820 --> 03:11.010
feels like someone I know.

03:14.260 --> 03:15.100
Lord Qi.

03:21.100 --> 03:22.170
No.

03:22.170 --> 03:23.130
It can't be Master.

03:24.260 --> 03:25.100
It's Li Wenxun.

03:31.100 --> 03:32.410
Where are the others?

03:33.096 --> 03:34.780
The Abbess brought
the surviving disciples

03:34.780 --> 03:36.410
to a safe place.

03:37.010 --> 03:38.380
Song Yuzhi and Fan Xingjia

03:38.380 --> 03:39.690
returned to Qingque Town.

03:41.260 --> 03:43.060
They took the Jade Sunflower.

03:43.540 --> 03:44.850
They also used Xingjia

03:44.850 --> 03:45.890
to take the Night Orchid.

03:46.980 --> 03:47.820
Now,

03:48.170 --> 03:50.260
with both the treasures,

03:50.850 --> 03:52.290
he will cultivate.

03:52.610 --> 03:54.130
If he masters the Ziwei Method,

03:54.660 --> 03:56.220
he will be the next Nie Hengcheng.

03:56.730 --> 03:57.570
No.

03:58.170 --> 03:59.890
We can't let

03:59.890 --> 04:00.820
the tragedy repeat.

04:02.410 --> 04:04.290
Are you going to risk your life
like your aunt?

04:04.290 --> 04:05.410
That's my choice.

04:06.850 --> 04:07.730
If I don't die,

04:08.940 --> 04:10.130
I'll repay

04:11.570 --> 04:12.820
today's life-saving favor.

04:15.010 --> 04:15.850
Let me go.

04:20.050 --> 04:20.890
What's wrong?

04:24.490 --> 04:26.020
I've stayed up several nights

04:26.020 --> 04:27.170
for an ingrate.

04:28.660 --> 04:29.660
I'm a little tired.

04:37.930 --> 04:38.770
Zhao,

04:39.660 --> 04:41.490
there won't be another Nie Hengcheng.

04:43.660 --> 04:45.700
He won't be able to master
the Ziwei Method.

04:52.290 --> 04:54.140
Mu Zhengyang is buried here.

04:54.900 --> 04:56.020
You found the body?

04:56.540 --> 04:58.100
When reorganizing Bliss Palace,

04:58.610 --> 05:00.100
we found a corpse in a stone cave

05:00.610 --> 05:01.810
near the underground palace.

05:01.962 --> 05:04.465
The fatal wound runs
from the left shoulder to the right rib.

05:04.610 --> 05:05.580
The sternum is broken.

05:06.170 --> 05:07.010
It's a blade wound.

05:07.540 --> 05:08.580
The Sunshine Blade.

05:10.743 --> 05:11.852
Ms. Cai must have chased him

05:11.863 --> 05:13.170
all the way near Bliss Palace,

05:14.170 --> 05:15.580
cornered Mu Zhengyang,

05:16.170 --> 05:17.340
and killed him on the spot.

05:18.290 --> 05:19.256
As for why Nie Hengcheng

05:19.267 --> 05:20.850
failed to master the Ziwei Method,

05:21.340 --> 05:22.580
the answer lies within.

05:25.540 --> 05:27.460
(Zhengyang)

05:27.930 --> 05:29.220
Mu Zhengyang's handbook?

05:31.980 --> 05:33.370
(Nie is treacherous.)

05:34.140 --> 05:35.820
(After torturing me
with a branding iron,)

05:35.900 --> 05:37.140
(he still wanted to kill me.)

05:37.140 --> 05:38.100
(Jiuzhou Archive)

05:38.100 --> 05:39.490
(My brother hid me)

05:40.140 --> 05:41.730
(in the Jiuzhou Archive.)

05:42.660 --> 05:43.500
(I got bored)

05:43.900 --> 05:44.900
(and read all the books.)

05:45.410 --> 05:47.490
(Unexpectedly, I found
the ancient Ziwei Method.)

05:50.170 --> 05:51.010
(It's said)

05:51.209 --> 05:53.165
(that the Founder's son wanted
to practice this,)

05:53.250 --> 05:54.780
(but he was forbidden.)

05:56.610 --> 05:58.340
(This method requires the life force)

05:59.170 --> 06:00.900
(of a close relative.)

06:01.850 --> 06:03.610
(Otherwise, one goes mad)

06:03.610 --> 06:04.660
(and dies.)

06:06.250 --> 06:07.580
(To avenge past shame,)

06:08.540 --> 06:09.900
(I lured Nie Hengcheng)

06:10.490 --> 06:11.730
(to practice the Ziwei Method.)

06:13.140 --> 06:14.490
(But the necessary saliva)

06:15.170 --> 06:16.730
(and the Night Orchid)

06:17.850 --> 06:19.980
(are connected
to the Luoying demoness.)

06:20.980 --> 06:21.820
(So,)

06:23.100 --> 06:24.980
(I deliberately approached Pingshu.)

06:28.900 --> 06:29.740
(Later,)

06:30.810 --> 06:32.730
(Pingshu's friends, the Shi brothers,)

06:32.730 --> 06:34.170
(were poisoned by the Nether Aura.)

06:34.980 --> 06:37.410
(They urgently needed
the Jade Sunflower.)

06:38.370 --> 06:39.850
(I told her my identity)

06:40.540 --> 06:42.050
(and stole it for her)

06:42.780 --> 06:44.100
(to gain her trust.)

06:45.930 --> 06:47.340
You'll kill Nie Hengcheng?

06:47.850 --> 06:49.100
As long as I get the saliva,

06:49.490 --> 06:50.456
I can increase my power,

06:51.050 --> 06:52.340
kill Nie Hengcheng,

06:52.340 --> 06:53.290
and reclaim the Li Sect.

06:54.020 --> 06:54.980
At that time,

06:54.980 --> 06:56.490
the Six Sects and Li Sect

06:56.490 --> 06:57.980
will lay down arms

06:59.020 --> 06:59.900
and restore peace

07:00.700 --> 07:01.900
to Jianghu.

07:08.980 --> 07:09.980
The saliva is

07:10.930 --> 07:11.816
in the snow mountains.

07:32.370 --> 07:34.100
ظآزIn days gone byظآز

07:34.410 --> 07:35.960
ظآزWillows swayed gentlyظآز

07:36.260 --> 07:39.010
ظآزI first saw you in the dimnessظآز

07:39.980 --> 07:41.170
ظآزAmid the vast crowdظآز

07:41.180 --> 07:42.650
ظآزA fleeting glanceظآز

07:42.820 --> 07:43.730
ظآزAnd thenظآز

07:43.740 --> 07:46.690
ظآزLove consumed meظآز

07:47.500 --> 07:49.050
ظآزNow I think of youظآز

07:49.450 --> 07:51.090
ظآزSnow and rain fall thicklyظآز

07:51.350 --> 07:52.690
ظآزAlas, we partedظآز

07:52.700 --> 07:54.890
ظآزLonging for your returnظآز

07:55.020 --> 07:55.970
ظآزMoon waxes and wanesظآز

07:55.980 --> 07:57.450
ظآزLetters can't convey my thoughtsظآز

07:57.460 --> 07:58.490
ظآزScattered petalsظآز

07:58.500 --> 08:00.730
ظآزCover the groundظآز

08:01.590 --> 08:04.050
ظآزSuch should be our meetingظآز

08:06.100 --> 08:08.900
Irises will bring you luck.

08:08.930 --> 08:11.650
ظآزHalf shy, half joyfulظآز

08:11.910 --> 08:15.850
ظآزWanting to leave yet lingeringظآز

08:16.570 --> 08:19.100
ظآزSuch should be our meetingظآز

08:19.380 --> 08:23.630
ظآزAcross the Magpie Bridgeظآز

08:24.700 --> 08:26.100
It's the irises.

08:26.100 --> 08:27.320
They'll bring you luck.

08:27.330 --> 08:31.230
ظآزTears are like pearlsظآز

08:47.400 --> 08:49.730
ظآزThings stay, yet you're awayظآز

08:50.110 --> 08:54.330
ظآزWho will hear the broken stringsظآز

08:54.870 --> 08:56.970
ظآزAcross the starry skiesظآز

08:57.350 --> 09:02.230
ظآزI see your shadow thereظآز

09:02.390 --> 09:05.170
ظآزSuch should be our meetingظآز

09:05.170 --> 09:09.650
ظآزGolden wind brushes the jade dewظآز

09:09.900 --> 09:12.510
ظآزHalf shy, half joyfulظآز

09:12.720 --> 09:16.820
ظآزWanting to leave yet lingeringظآز

09:17.850 --> 09:18.690
(Later,)

09:19.530 --> 09:20.980
(I roamed Jianghu with her.)

09:21.700 --> 09:22.730
(She accompanied me)

09:22.730 --> 09:24.100
(to find the Night Orchid.)

09:25.420 --> 09:26.700
(I enjoyed)

09:27.300 --> 09:28.890
(my comfortable time with her.)

09:36.160 --> 09:38.550
ظآزSuch should be our meetingظآز

09:38.980 --> 09:42.230
ظآزAcross the Magpie Bridgeظآز

09:43.730 --> 09:44.730
Master Zhengyang,

09:45.100 --> 09:47.850
feelings should be expressed.

10:02.650 --> 10:04.420
(If not for the unresolved feud,)

10:06.010 --> 10:07.850
(I'd want to be with her forever.)

10:29.130 --> 10:30.180
(As expected,)

10:31.183 --> 10:32.300
(Nie Hengcheng lost control)

10:32.300 --> 10:33.980
(after reaching the third level)

10:34.650 --> 10:35.556
(of the Ziwei Method,)

10:36.340 --> 10:37.700
(harming martial artists.)

10:39.580 --> 10:41.820
(Yin Dai of Qingque Sect
led a battle against him.)

10:42.890 --> 10:44.650
(I intended to benefit from it.)

10:45.610 --> 10:46.450
(Unexpectedly,)

10:46.610 --> 10:47.850
(Pingshu, a junior,)

10:48.180 --> 10:49.440
(together with several friends)

10:50.180 --> 10:52.100
(improved the Big Dipper Formation,)

10:52.890 --> 10:54.890
(planning to use it to kill Nie.)

10:57.180 --> 10:58.770
Must you go to kill him now?

10:58.770 --> 11:00.100
Nie's crimes are unforgivable.

11:01.100 --> 11:02.700
Even if it costs my life,

11:02.700 --> 11:03.586
he must be eliminated.

11:06.100 --> 11:07.300
Since you've decided,

11:08.340 --> 11:09.180
I'll accompany you.

11:10.530 --> 11:11.650
But before that,

11:13.980 --> 11:14.980
let's get married.

11:18.490 --> 11:19.330
Okay.

11:25.700 --> 11:26.850
(We made marriage vows)

11:27.580 --> 11:28.730
(and bound our love.)

11:30.220 --> 11:32.610
(I also learned the whereabouts
of Pingshu's friends)

11:34.420 --> 11:35.940
(and planned an ambush for them.)

11:42.890 --> 11:44.580
He intended to kill Nie Hengcheng,

11:45.770 --> 11:47.300
so why harm my aunt's friends?

11:47.980 --> 11:48.890
For power.

11:49.220 --> 11:50.370
For sole rule over the world.

11:50.820 --> 11:51.660
At that time,

11:51.890 --> 11:53.300
Nie Hengcheng was going mad.

11:53.610 --> 11:54.580
He was near death.

11:54.580 --> 11:56.060
My father wouldn't contest.

11:56.610 --> 11:59.100
He only needed
to eliminate Nie's remnants

11:59.730 --> 12:01.700
to become the Chief.

12:01.700 --> 12:03.266
Mu Zhengyang feared no one like Yin Dai,

12:03.820 --> 12:05.610
but he feared your aunt

12:05.610 --> 12:07.340
and her friends.

12:07.820 --> 12:09.250
They were top-tier martial artists.

12:09.850 --> 12:11.580
If they formed
a seven-person sword array,

12:11.890 --> 12:12.890
how could he resist?

12:13.250 --> 12:14.820
So, he killed them early.

12:15.490 --> 12:16.850
But he never expected

12:17.770 --> 12:19.650
Lu Chengnan to betray the sect.

12:20.100 --> 12:21.770
After being gravely injured,

12:21.770 --> 12:23.063
Lu Chengnan escaped to Chang Fort

12:23.770 --> 12:25.010
and revealed the Ziwei Method

12:25.010 --> 12:27.340
and Nie Hengcheng's secrets to my aunt.

12:29.730 --> 12:31.580
Mu Zhengyang lost everything.

12:32.060 --> 12:32.900
Indeed.

12:33.300 --> 12:34.890
My aunt must have been heartbroken

12:37.060 --> 12:38.300
upon learning the truth.

13:51.450 --> 13:55.160
ظآزLifeظآز

13:55.170 --> 13:57.590
ظآزPasses swiftlyظآز

13:58.380 --> 14:00.270
ظآزTime is longظآز

14:00.280 --> 14:02.020
ظآزPleasures are fewظآز

14:02.030 --> 14:05.830
ظآزToo many days lostظآز

14:05.850 --> 14:10.020
ظآزHow many loversظآز

14:10.030 --> 14:13.560
ظآزOnce stood side by side
through hardshipsظآز

14:13.620 --> 14:15.140
ظآزIn the endظآز

14:15.150 --> 14:20.140
ظآزThey forget each otherظآز

14:20.140 --> 14:23.120
ظآزFateظآز

14:23.340 --> 14:26.810
ظآزPasses swiftlyظآز

14:26.980 --> 14:28.930
ظآزLiquor is strongظآز

14:28.940 --> 14:30.920
ظآزChests are warmظآز

14:30.930 --> 14:34.770
ظآزLoyalty turns coldظآز

14:34.770 --> 14:40.230
ظآزMany affections are hard to severظآز

14:40.710 --> 14:44.350
ظآزLeaving only meظآز

14:46.250 --> 14:47.850
(I don't regret what I did.)

14:49.650 --> 14:51.060
(I only feel indebted)

14:52.300 --> 14:53.420
(to Zhengming and Pingshu.)

14:56.370 --> 14:57.370
(In fact, Nie Hengcheng)

14:57.820 --> 14:58.850
(didn't know that mastery)

14:58.850 --> 15:01.650
(requires a relative's life force,)

15:01.650 --> 15:03.420
(so he'd die within three years.)

15:04.130 --> 15:05.420
(But Pingshu's temperament)

15:06.370 --> 15:07.730
(won't allow her to wait.)

15:10.300 --> 15:11.420
(Perhaps one day,)

15:12.610 --> 15:14.340
(I can apologize to her
in the underworld.)

15:27.010 --> 15:28.060
A relative's life force?

15:28.850 --> 15:29.940
The Ziwei Method,

15:30.370 --> 15:31.250
dragon beast saliva,

15:31.580 --> 15:32.420
the Night Orchid,

15:32.650 --> 15:33.700
and the Jade Sunflower

15:33.700 --> 15:34.770
are all indispensable.

15:35.300 --> 15:36.340
The final step requires

15:37.770 --> 15:39.130
the Jade Sunflower

15:39.130 --> 15:40.730
to absorb bloodline energy.

15:42.180 --> 15:43.850
Without it, one goes mad and dies.

15:45.060 --> 15:46.180
This is why the Founder

15:46.180 --> 15:47.130
forbade the Ziwei Method

15:47.130 --> 15:48.700
from spreading,

15:49.940 --> 15:50.890
and the secret

15:51.530 --> 15:52.483
Mu Zhengyang discovered.

15:54.300 --> 15:55.140
Zhao,

15:55.610 --> 15:57.130
my father was once injured

15:58.770 --> 16:00.300
by Mu Zhengyang

16:00.300 --> 16:01.700
because he tried to seize me

16:01.700 --> 16:03.300
as an infant.

16:03.300 --> 16:04.610
I never understood

16:04.980 --> 16:05.980
why he'd do this

16:06.610 --> 16:08.370
until I found his handbook.

16:08.370 --> 16:09.650
I was the one

16:10.530 --> 16:12.490
he had been targeting as close kin.

16:14.370 --> 16:15.700
If the man in black

16:16.060 --> 16:17.250
doesn't know the final step,

16:18.300 --> 16:20.010
he'll go mad and die

16:20.420 --> 16:21.300
like Nie Hengcheng.

16:21.980 --> 16:22.820
Yes.

16:23.700 --> 16:24.820
What we need now

16:25.940 --> 16:26.890
is to wait.

16:27.940 --> 16:28.820
Wait?

16:30.556 --> 16:32.862
Wait for him to go on a killing spree
like Nie Hengcheng?

16:34.890 --> 16:36.010
Do you know why

16:36.580 --> 16:37.420
my aunt,

16:38.100 --> 16:40.060
knowing Nie Hengcheng would die,

16:40.530 --> 16:42.420
still went to Mount Tu to kill him?

16:43.250 --> 16:44.090
Zhao.

16:44.250 --> 16:45.100
Aunt once said,

16:45.610 --> 16:47.220
"There are two kinds of evil people."

16:48.040 --> 16:48.890
"One is the one"

16:48.890 --> 16:49.890
"who commits evil."

16:50.300 --> 16:51.173
"The other is the one"

16:52.180 --> 16:53.980
"who stands by and watches."

16:55.060 --> 16:56.980
I may not be a great heroine
like my aunt,

16:58.220 --> 16:59.650
but I can't stand aside.

17:00.250 --> 17:01.730
Turning a blind eye for a moment

17:01.730 --> 17:03.490
will only bring a lifetime of unrest.

17:04.570 --> 17:05.810
This deal can't be done.

17:17.050 --> 17:17.890
Zhao,

17:19.010 --> 17:21.010
he's reached the third level.

17:21.770 --> 17:22.860
You can't beat him.

17:23.330 --> 17:24.490
So what?

17:27.010 --> 17:28.380
Chivalry requires

17:28.380 --> 17:30.290
attempting the impossible,

17:31.620 --> 17:32.460
right?

17:35.380 --> 17:36.220
Mu Qingyan,

17:37.180 --> 17:38.090
don't stop me.

17:39.380 --> 17:40.770
I don't want us to end up

17:41.940 --> 17:45.250
like Mu Zhengyang and my aunt.

18:13.660 --> 18:14.500
Aunt,

18:15.570 --> 18:18.620
was the Founder really a disciple
of an immortal?

18:22.090 --> 18:23.620
That was centuries ago.

18:24.090 --> 18:25.660
I don't know if it's true.

18:26.900 --> 18:28.940
But as disciples of the Beichen lineage,

18:29.570 --> 18:31.700
we have to give the Founder some honor.

18:32.330 --> 18:34.730
Do you want it to be true or false?

18:34.730 --> 18:36.180
I hope it's false.

18:36.730 --> 18:37.570
Why?

18:37.570 --> 18:40.090
All the other immortals flew to heaven,

18:40.090 --> 18:43.980
leaving only the Founder
in the mortal world.

18:43.980 --> 18:45.730
He must've been pitiful.

18:45.730 --> 18:47.730
You're too kindhearted

18:47.730 --> 18:49.900
to roam Jianghu in the future.

19:23.810 --> 19:24.650
Young Master!

19:26.090 --> 19:26.930
Young Master.

19:37.220 --> 19:38.090
Young Master,

19:38.620 --> 19:39.730
this kind of medicine

19:39.730 --> 19:41.420
is just a desperate, harmful cure.

19:41.420 --> 19:42.660
You can't take it.

19:43.700 --> 19:44.540
It's fine.

19:45.860 --> 19:47.420
I don't have much time anyway.

19:48.330 --> 19:50.050
I could've thought of other ways,

19:50.700 --> 19:52.330
but you insist...

19:52.330 --> 19:53.250
Alright, Uncle Cheng.

19:56.570 --> 19:57.940
I won't die

19:59.660 --> 20:00.860
without seeing the end.

20:07.010 --> 20:07.850
Young Master.

20:19.380 --> 20:20.420
Zhuang?

20:20.860 --> 20:21.900
Today, you'll come with me.

20:21.900 --> 20:22.740
Okay.

20:24.860 --> 20:25.700
Zhao.

20:33.660 --> 20:35.020
- Xingjia.
- Zhao.

20:36.420 --> 20:37.930
Xingjia, sit.

20:38.140 --> 20:39.010
How's your leg?

20:39.010 --> 20:40.530
I'm fine, Zhao.

20:40.530 --> 20:42.010
It's great to see you back safely.

20:42.770 --> 20:44.330
Where is Abbess Jingyuan? How is she?

20:44.330 --> 20:45.290
She's badly injured

20:45.290 --> 20:46.349
but not in mortal danger.

20:46.360 --> 20:47.773
She's been taken care of to recover.

20:48.090 --> 20:49.940
We've sent messages to all sects.

20:49.940 --> 20:52.380
Lord Cai and the others
should arrive soon.

20:55.770 --> 20:56.860
Zhao,

20:56.860 --> 20:58.243
the people who attacked us

20:58.254 --> 21:00.000
- at Xuankong Nunnery...
- Uncle Li, right?

21:03.660 --> 21:04.500
Zhao,

21:04.940 --> 21:06.620
the man in black really was Uncle Li?

21:07.180 --> 21:08.929
He said he had a headache,

21:08.940 --> 21:10.380
so I gave him the remaining essence

21:10.380 --> 21:11.380
to treat it.

21:11.700 --> 21:12.900
I didn't know.

21:13.330 --> 21:14.420
I really didn't know.

21:15.810 --> 21:16.730
I suspect

21:17.050 --> 21:19.140
Master has been deceived by Uncle Li.

21:19.810 --> 21:21.250
Now, Qingque Town is full

21:21.250 --> 21:22.770
of Siqi and Guangtian members.

21:22.770 --> 21:25.220
Yang Heying and Song Xiuzhi
have climbed the mountain,

21:25.220 --> 21:26.556
blaming everything on Mu Qingyan,

21:26.567 --> 21:28.566
and claiming the demonic sect
is about to attack.

21:28.577 --> 21:29.417
Qingque Sect

21:30.010 --> 21:31.180
is now on high alert.

21:31.490 --> 21:32.700
These thugs

21:33.050 --> 21:34.010
always twist the truth.

21:34.330 --> 21:35.170
Zhao,

21:35.490 --> 21:36.620
with the situation so tense,

21:36.620 --> 21:37.980
should we ask Mr. Mu for help?

21:41.090 --> 21:42.156
We should solve the problem

21:42.940 --> 21:44.250
of the Six Sects ourselves.

21:46.010 --> 21:46.850
Yuzhi,

21:47.050 --> 21:48.220
we'll climb the mountain

21:48.860 --> 21:49.800
to find Master tonight.

22:00.663 --> 22:01.620
The iron chain mechanism

22:01.620 --> 22:03.250
is usually guarded by trusted disciples.

22:03.676 --> 22:05.062
How could it be left to outsiders?

22:05.860 --> 22:06.730
It seems Fengchi

22:07.050 --> 22:07.890
and Zhuo

22:08.770 --> 22:10.140
have been controlled by Uncle Li.

22:15.745 --> 22:17.258
(Pillar of Jianghu)
What demonic sect?

22:17.620 --> 22:20.330
Yang Heying made the corpse slaves.

22:20.330 --> 22:21.170
You...

22:22.090 --> 22:24.010
You've been deceived too?

22:27.580 --> 22:31.820
(Righteous Spirit)

22:51.530 --> 22:52.370
You...

22:52.660 --> 22:53.620
Why are you doing this?

23:03.380 --> 23:04.220
- Master!
- Master!

23:06.220 --> 23:07.060
Zhao,

23:07.380 --> 23:08.220
Yuzhi,

23:08.900 --> 23:09.740
why are you here?

23:10.810 --> 23:12.250
I've been worried about you.

23:15.050 --> 23:16.290
Master,

23:18.570 --> 23:19.860
what are you doing?

23:24.770 --> 23:25.900
Why?

23:29.940 --> 23:31.010
I'm only doing this

23:32.620 --> 23:34.250
to avenge Pingshu.

23:37.290 --> 23:38.490
For my aunt?

23:38.490 --> 23:40.180
I won't spare anyone

23:40.860 --> 23:42.810
who wronged your aunt.

23:44.050 --> 23:46.010
If he hadn't treated Pingshu badly,

23:46.010 --> 23:47.860
she wouldn't have left Peiqiong Manor

23:48.420 --> 23:50.660
and wouldn't have encountered
Mu Zhengyang's schemes.

23:52.570 --> 23:54.140
You did this for that?

23:54.770 --> 23:55.980
But Qi,

23:56.660 --> 23:58.700
I didn't cancel

23:58.700 --> 23:59.810
the betrothal.

24:01.220 --> 24:02.530
I had feelings

24:03.700 --> 24:05.290
for Pingshu.

24:05.290 --> 24:06.130
I know

24:07.530 --> 24:09.570
you marrying someone else
was Pingshu's idea.

24:10.010 --> 24:11.380
I didn't blame you then.

24:11.860 --> 24:13.290
But later, I realized

24:14.140 --> 24:15.810
you hurt Pingshu's heart,

24:15.810 --> 24:17.250
so she canceled the betrothal.

24:18.140 --> 24:19.250
Zhao, tell me.

24:19.250 --> 24:20.220
Should such a person

24:20.220 --> 24:21.220
be killed?

24:25.090 --> 24:26.940
You really are the man in black.

24:36.660 --> 24:38.770
But what did Uncle Chang do wrong?

24:39.730 --> 24:41.490
Why slaughter his whole clan?

24:41.490 --> 24:42.900
Because he tried to stop me

24:42.900 --> 24:44.050
from avenging your aunt.

24:45.180 --> 24:46.193
Why leave him alive?

24:47.700 --> 24:50.380
When you joined forces
to protect Luoying Valley,

24:52.180 --> 24:54.860
you'd risk your lives for each other.

24:55.220 --> 24:56.490
So, you also injured my father,

24:56.900 --> 24:59.570
staged the Guangtian strife,

24:59.940 --> 25:01.490
and killed the nuns

25:01.490 --> 25:02.570
at Xuankong Nunnery.

25:03.530 --> 25:05.220
Master, why did you do this?

25:05.710 --> 25:07.876
Is it all for the Night Orchid
and the Jade Sunflower?

25:08.660 --> 25:10.220
For practicing the Ziwei Method?

25:10.220 --> 25:11.250
I'm doing this

25:13.770 --> 25:16.220
to fulfill Pingshu's last wish.

25:16.900 --> 25:18.620
Pingshu always wanted

25:18.620 --> 25:20.330
a Jianghu filled
with chivalry and justice,

25:20.330 --> 25:22.420
where anyone could stand up.

25:22.420 --> 25:24.700
Once I master the Ziwei Method,

25:24.700 --> 25:26.620
I'll kill all the hypocrites

25:26.620 --> 25:27.530
who harmed Pingshu,

25:27.530 --> 25:29.660
then hand over a clean Jianghu

25:29.660 --> 25:30.770
to you,

25:30.770 --> 25:31.610
okay?

25:36.980 --> 25:39.010
That's not what Aunt wanted.

25:39.420 --> 25:41.730
She died to kill Nie Hengcheng.

25:42.570 --> 25:43.696
She wouldn't want to see you

25:43.707 --> 25:45.530
become the second Nie Hengcheng.

25:45.860 --> 25:48.010
I won't become the second Nie Hengcheng.

25:48.530 --> 25:49.576
Nie Hengcheng didn't know

25:49.587 --> 25:51.220
the final step of the Ziwei Method,

25:51.220 --> 25:52.060
but I did.

25:54.900 --> 25:55.740
You...

25:56.330 --> 25:57.180
You knew?

26:00.090 --> 26:01.900
Are you going to do this to Lingbo?

26:05.880 --> 26:06.750
Zhao...

26:06.760 --> 26:08.980
You killed Pingshu's best friends,

26:10.140 --> 26:14.010
yet you claim it's to avenge her?

26:14.620 --> 26:17.290
You're putting Pingshu on the fire.

26:18.420 --> 26:20.570
Even if it costs my life,

26:21.700 --> 26:24.010
I'll stop you from using Pingshu's name

26:24.810 --> 26:27.050
to commit these cruel deeds.

26:27.050 --> 26:28.090
Best friends?

26:29.290 --> 26:30.420
Chang Haosheng,

26:30.420 --> 26:31.660
Song Shijun,

26:31.660 --> 26:33.420
and Abbess Jingyuan.

26:33.420 --> 26:35.530
Pingshu treated them as friends,

26:35.530 --> 26:36.810
risked her life for them,

26:36.810 --> 26:37.730
yet what did they do?

26:38.660 --> 26:39.810
After she died,

26:40.810 --> 26:43.420
they hid comfortably

26:43.420 --> 26:45.330
and never sought revenge.

26:45.330 --> 26:47.140
You hypocrites

26:48.220 --> 26:49.140
all deserve to die.

26:49.140 --> 26:50.380
You're insane!

26:51.770 --> 26:53.090
Master, no!

26:53.090 --> 26:54.540
Zhao, go!

26:54.980 --> 26:56.050
No one leaves.

26:56.050 --> 26:56.890
Go!

27:00.010 --> 27:00.850
Uncle Zhou!

27:09.290 --> 27:10.130
Song Yuzhi!

27:10.660 --> 27:11.500
Song Yuzhi!

27:12.530 --> 27:13.900
Song Yuzhi, open the door!

27:26.700 --> 27:27.570
Lingbo!

27:51.330 --> 27:52.170
Nanny Mao?

27:52.570 --> 27:53.420
Yes.

27:53.420 --> 27:54.570
Go see what's happening.

27:55.010 --> 27:55.850
It's...

28:18.980 --> 28:20.860
It's the demonic sect's alarm bell.

28:22.090 --> 28:23.090
Someone!

28:25.770 --> 28:26.900
Let us out!

28:27.530 --> 28:29.250
They drugged us heavily

28:30.900 --> 28:32.380
to trap us.

28:32.380 --> 28:33.860
Save your energy.

28:34.220 --> 28:35.060
Who?

28:36.220 --> 28:38.220
Why trap us here?

28:38.660 --> 28:39.570
I fear it's more

28:42.620 --> 28:44.140
than just the demonic sect.

29:04.660 --> 29:05.500
Isn't it fun?

29:20.980 --> 29:22.140
Greetings, Master.

29:22.860 --> 29:24.900
(Righteous Spirit)
Zhao is my personal disciple

29:24.900 --> 29:26.570
from Luoying Valley.

29:26.570 --> 29:28.700
Today, she officially joins us,

29:28.700 --> 29:29.810
ranking seventh.

29:29.810 --> 29:31.700
Congrats, Master. Congrats, Zhao.

29:32.330 --> 29:34.330
Everyone, please guide me.

29:34.980 --> 29:36.290
Zhao is my disciple.

29:36.730 --> 29:38.010
I can vouch for her.

29:38.330 --> 29:39.980
Until the truth is uncovered,

29:40.570 --> 29:41.700
no one

29:42.420 --> 29:43.770
may speak ill of Zhao.

29:45.140 --> 29:46.180
In life,

29:46.700 --> 29:48.730
there are times beyond one's control.

29:49.770 --> 29:51.140
Only by becoming strong

29:52.050 --> 29:53.250
can one be free.

30:00.220 --> 30:01.060
Aunt,

30:02.290 --> 30:03.770
what should I do?

30:14.680 --> 30:15.530
Search!

30:15.530 --> 30:16.370
- Yes.
- Yes.

30:18.770 --> 30:19.610
Where is she?

30:20.290 --> 30:21.940
Cai Zhao hid in the secret realm.

30:22.980 --> 30:24.290
By the time we pursued her,

30:25.050 --> 30:26.090
she was gone.

30:30.940 --> 30:31.780
Yunke,

30:32.660 --> 30:34.010
this can't be hidden any longer.

30:34.770 --> 30:35.660
The sooner we act,

30:36.770 --> 30:37.770
the better.

30:44.090 --> 30:44.930
Understood.

30:45.900 --> 30:46.740
Lady Yin.

30:48.530 --> 30:49.730
You arrived just in time.

30:49.730 --> 30:50.838
Why did the alarm bell sound

30:50.849 --> 30:51.810
for no reason?

30:51.810 --> 30:53.140
The demonic sect attacked

30:53.140 --> 30:54.330
and killed Lord Zhou.

30:55.660 --> 30:56.570
How could this happen?

30:57.810 --> 30:58.700
What about your master?

30:59.490 --> 31:00.330
He's safe.

31:00.570 --> 31:01.660
The invaders were repelled,

31:02.090 --> 31:03.730
but some

31:04.330 --> 31:05.660
may still be in the mountains.

31:06.050 --> 31:07.620
Master instructed me to tell you

31:08.050 --> 31:09.490
to stay here

31:09.860 --> 31:10.810
and not go wandering.

31:12.810 --> 31:13.650
Understood.

31:14.490 --> 31:15.330
Where's Lingbo?

31:15.620 --> 31:17.010
She went to see Fengchi today.

31:17.250 --> 31:19.050
She's upset that he left to do his job

31:19.420 --> 31:21.660
without saying goodbye,

31:22.050 --> 31:23.380
staying inside sulking.

31:24.380 --> 31:25.220
Lady Yin,

31:25.490 --> 31:26.330
the two factions

31:27.290 --> 31:28.490
may face a great battle.

31:28.980 --> 31:30.180
You should take Lingbo

31:30.180 --> 31:31.860
and stay at the Yin estate for a while.

31:32.380 --> 31:33.420
Once things stabilize,

31:33.860 --> 31:34.810
I'll bring you back.

31:35.180 --> 31:36.980
I'm still the Lady.

31:37.330 --> 31:38.490
In danger,

31:38.490 --> 31:40.660
how could I abandon

31:40.660 --> 31:42.380
your master and you?

31:42.980 --> 31:43.940
Rest assured.

31:43.940 --> 31:45.220
I'll be careful

31:45.810 --> 31:46.776
and won't slow you down.

31:47.330 --> 31:48.170
Yes,

31:48.770 --> 31:49.610
Lady Yin.

32:15.220 --> 32:16.090
Lingbo!

32:17.220 --> 32:18.060
Lingbo!

32:22.430 --> 32:23.290
Make way.

32:23.290 --> 32:24.130
I'm going out!

32:31.700 --> 32:33.250
How dare you hit me?

32:33.570 --> 32:34.730
Someone, help!

32:35.010 --> 32:36.090
Help!

32:36.090 --> 32:37.380
They hit me!

32:37.380 --> 32:38.980
Lingbo, what's wrong?

32:39.570 --> 32:41.290
Dalou!

32:42.090 --> 32:43.010
He hit me.

32:43.010 --> 32:43.980
And they.

32:44.330 --> 32:45.660
They hit me!

32:46.290 --> 32:48.050
I'll tell Father!

32:48.050 --> 32:50.050
I'll make Father stand up for me!

32:50.050 --> 32:50.890
Lingbo,

32:51.090 --> 32:52.620
Master is dealing with the demonic sect

32:53.180 --> 32:54.180
and can't leave.

32:54.860 --> 32:56.090
Everyone must help.

32:56.090 --> 32:56.940
Stop causing trouble.

33:00.850 --> 33:01.700
No!

33:01.700 --> 33:03.080
I want to see my father!

33:03.180 --> 33:04.380
I want to see my father!

33:04.380 --> 33:05.220
Lingbo.

33:11.220 --> 33:12.060
Tell me.

33:12.330 --> 33:14.090
Why sneak in?

33:14.570 --> 33:16.140
You made me fight them on purpose.

33:16.390 --> 33:17.709
Luckily, my acting is convincing.

33:18.380 --> 33:19.220
Lingbo,

33:21.010 --> 33:21.963
I have to take you away.

33:24.530 --> 33:25.530
Are you crazy?

33:25.530 --> 33:26.940
Why should I leave my home

33:26.940 --> 33:28.250
with a demoness like you?

33:29.380 --> 33:30.220
Zhao,

33:30.730 --> 33:32.050
do you know something?

33:39.420 --> 33:42.020
(Discipline Hall)

34:09.090 --> 34:09.930
Yuzhi,

34:11.050 --> 34:11.940
are you alright?

34:13.300 --> 34:14.170
Master,

34:16.050 --> 34:18.090
Zhao will stop you.

34:18.420 --> 34:20.090
Why?

34:22.010 --> 34:22.850
Tell me.

34:23.860 --> 34:25.010
Don't you want

34:25.010 --> 34:27.050
a clean Jianghu?

34:27.050 --> 34:29.490
A Jianghu won through killing

34:30.130 --> 34:31.650
can't be clean.

34:31.900 --> 34:33.090
This Jianghu

34:33.690 --> 34:35.530
is already rotten.

34:37.380 --> 34:38.570
Pingshu said

34:39.980 --> 34:41.090
that for over 200 years,

34:41.980 --> 34:43.090
the Six Sects

34:43.650 --> 34:45.650
had grown stagnant,

34:45.650 --> 34:47.090
stuck in old ways.

34:47.490 --> 34:48.940
Many ambitious youths,

34:49.900 --> 34:51.570
born into low status,

34:52.050 --> 34:54.010
couldn't rise

34:54.010 --> 34:55.610
and were suppressed.

34:56.130 --> 34:57.490
Shouldn't this Jianghu

34:58.690 --> 35:00.210
change?

35:00.210 --> 35:01.530
You mean

35:03.380 --> 35:05.820
by killing them all?

35:05.820 --> 35:06.660
Yes.

35:08.570 --> 35:09.570
Break to build.

35:10.650 --> 35:12.380
From ruin to renewal.

35:12.380 --> 35:14.170
Taichu Temple is gone;

35:14.170 --> 35:16.210
Siqi Sect is nearly destroyed.

35:16.210 --> 35:18.490
Chaos at Peiqiong Manor is imminent.

35:18.490 --> 35:20.340
Guangtian Sect can't be left behind.

35:21.010 --> 35:22.210
Luoying Valley

35:23.130 --> 35:25.170
has always lived in seclusion.

35:25.610 --> 35:27.740
I'll leave Qingque Sect.

35:28.210 --> 35:29.050
Then,

35:29.490 --> 35:31.260
the Six Sects combined

35:31.260 --> 35:32.690
will be handed to you and Zhao.

35:32.690 --> 35:33.530
Agreed?

35:33.530 --> 35:34.980
You've done so many evil deeds.

35:35.650 --> 35:38.170
How will Jianghu see our sect?

35:38.170 --> 35:39.010
Easy.

35:40.860 --> 35:41.860
Once I clear

35:42.340 --> 35:44.050
all obstacles,

35:44.610 --> 35:45.740
take my head

35:46.530 --> 35:48.300
to honor the dead,

35:48.300 --> 35:49.420
and use my blood

35:50.170 --> 35:51.940
to cleanse the sect's shame.

35:52.570 --> 35:53.410
Let me

35:54.010 --> 35:55.050
be infamous forever.

35:55.420 --> 35:56.340
Only then

35:57.340 --> 35:58.980
will Jianghu submit to you.

35:58.980 --> 35:59.830
No.

35:59.840 --> 36:01.260
We don't want this Jianghu.

36:01.260 --> 36:02.650
I only want my old master.

36:03.260 --> 36:04.690
Master, do you remember?

36:05.170 --> 36:07.340
When I joined, you warned me

36:08.210 --> 36:09.690
not to fear the strong,

36:10.170 --> 36:11.090
not to bully the weak,

36:11.479 --> 36:13.492
not to kill recklessly,
and not to act arrogantly.

36:13.610 --> 36:14.490
My master

36:14.490 --> 36:15.820
would never kill my father,

36:16.260 --> 36:18.420
nor Mr. Chang or Lord Zhou.

36:19.050 --> 36:20.610
It's not too late.

36:21.380 --> 36:22.420
Please stop, Master.

36:22.420 --> 36:23.820
Stop, Master.

36:31.170 --> 36:32.050
Yuzhi,

36:33.260 --> 36:34.530
you haven't failed

36:34.530 --> 36:36.490
all these years of my guidance.

36:36.900 --> 36:38.300
You haven't disappointed me.

36:39.820 --> 36:40.940
I'm at ease.

36:42.260 --> 36:43.100
Master...

36:44.570 --> 36:45.410
Master...

36:45.690 --> 36:47.130
I beg you to stop, Master.

36:47.780 --> 36:48.620
Master...

36:50.090 --> 36:51.740
Master!

37:00.561 --> 37:11.221
=Generation to Generation=

